<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450504>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Neoconis szirakii sp. n., male. (A, B) habitus, dorsal; (C, D, E) genitalia, dorsal; (F, G) genitalia, lateral; (H) genitalia, ventral; (I, J, K) genitalia, caudal; (L) internal genitalia, ventrolateral; (M) internal genitalia, lateral. A = holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450504/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450508>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Aleuropteryx spp. (A) A. maculipennis, male habitus, lateral; (B) A. maculipennis, male genitalia, lateral; (C) A. maculipennis, male internal genitalia, ventral; (D) A. simillima, male habitus, lateral; (E) A. simillima, male internal genitalia, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450508/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450506>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Coniopteryx josephus sp. n., male. (A, B) habitus, lateral; (C, D) genitalia, lateral; (E, F) genitalia, caudal; (G, H) hypandrium, ventral; (I, J) genitalia, dorsal; (K) internal genitalia, dorsal; (L) genitalia, ventral; (M) paramere and penis, lateral. J, L = holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450506/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450510>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Coniopteryx (C.) spp., male. (A) C. minuta, habitus, lateral; (B) C. minuta, genitalia, lateral; (C) C. palpalis, habitus, lateral; (D) C. palpalis, genitalia, lateral; (E) C. palpalis, genitalia, caudal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450510/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450514>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Coniopteryx spp., male. (A) C. (C.) westwoodi, habitus, lateral; (B) C. (C.) westwoodi, genitalia, ventro-caudal; (C) C. (Xeroconiopteryx) diversicornis, habitus, lateral; (D) C. (X.) diversicornis, genitalia, caudal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450514/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450516>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Coniopterygidae spp., male. (A) Parasemidalis fuscipennis, habitus, lateral; (B) P. fuscipennis, genitalia, lateral; (C) Conwentzia barretti, habitus, lateral; (D) C. barretti, genitalia, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450516/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450520>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Semidalis spp., male. (A) S. arnaudi, habitus, lateral; (B) S. arnaudi, genitalia, lateral; (C) S. hidalgoana, habitus, lateral; (D) S. hidalgoana, genitalia, lateral; (E) S. hidalgoana, genitalia, caudal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450520/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

